asset.title: 2011, 2012, 2013 & 2014 Chevy Camaro 3.6L Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
See how easy it is to add more performance to the 2011, 2012 and 2013 Chevy Camaro with the 3.6L engine.

http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-3078

This K&N air intake modification showed an estimated gain of 11.4 horsepower at 5800 RPM when tested on the K&N dynamometer. 

K&N 63-3078 fits the following: 
2014 CHEVROLET CAMARO 3.6L V6 F/I - All 
2013 CHEVROLET CAMARO 3.6L V6 F/I - All 
2012 CHEVROLET CAMARO 3.6L V6 F/I - All 
2011 CHEVROLET CAMARO 3.6L V6 F/I - All 
 
Go to http://www.knfilters.com/search/product.aspx?prod=63-3078 for an up to date application list.

Search for your own vehicle's corresponding cold air intake and air filter here:
http://www.KNfilters.com
